import React from 'react';

import { BannerContainer, BannerTextBackgroundGreen, BannerTextBackgroundYellow, BannerTextBackgroundRed, BannerText } from './banner.styles';


const Banner = () => (
  <BannerContainer>
    <BannerTextBackgroundRed>
      <BannerText></BannerText>
    </BannerTextBackgroundRed>
    <BannerTextBackgroundYellow>
      <BannerText>Free Beats for Download</BannerText>
      <button>Get them Now!</button>
      <BannerText>Fresh Beats For Sale</BannerText>
      <button>Listen Now</button>
    </BannerTextBackgroundYellow>
    <BannerTextBackgroundGreen>
      <BannerText>Subscribe to get 20% Off Rates</BannerText>
      <button>Subscribe and Download Rate Sheet</button>
      <BannerText>Get Your Free Master</BannerText>
      <button>Get a Free Master</button>
    </BannerTextBackgroundGreen>
  </BannerContainer>

);

export default React.memo(Banner);
